    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Visual works created with real or simulated flexible twigs, osiers, canes, or the like that are woven and plaited together. Examples of wickerwork are baskets and furniture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
